Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:14.97,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:15.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:18.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:23.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:26.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:30.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:33.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:40.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:45.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:48.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:51.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:55.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:59.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:03.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:11.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:15.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:18.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.97,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,150.389)}The Man-Eating Flower
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.97,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(567.167,660.389)}Dokudalian
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that one in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister really loves those...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.46,0:01:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're giving them to your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's her last birthday\Nbefore she gets married!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.72,0:01:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a much older big sister? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll give you this as a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a present from me to your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes thirteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:08.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This woman is the Shocker\Nmonster Dokudalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:10.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A 200 year old woman—no,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:14.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,a 200-year-old carnivorous flower\Nfrom the jungles of New Guinea,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:16.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,converted into a monster by Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget this beautiful bouquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sis, you're all sentimental...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you're getting married\Ndoesn't mean we're not sisters anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:09.93,Italics,,0,0,0,,Sleep... sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:14.54,Italics,,0,0,0,,Now, collapse, and sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko! Akko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The sleep waves worked, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello, turtle man!\NTurtle man, my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a weird uniform for a taxi driver...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't refuse service to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... that's assault,\Nyou know! It's not nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:15.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The terrible man-eating flowers\Nof New Guinea earn their name
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:19.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,from the way they draw in\Nand absorb any humans who get near.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:24.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In other words, they break down\Nanimal proteins to sustain themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You now work for Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:59.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's reason for kidnapping all\Nwomen was to have them create poisons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:02.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Delicate fingers were required\Nto create crystallized poison
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,from the poison flower extract.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison flower extract is pouring in\Nfrom our New Guinea Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnap more women, and proceed\Nquickly with creating the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost finished, Colonel Zol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One drop of a suspension of this\Npoison can kill one hundred people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If we convert that suspension into a mist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and disperse it secretly\Nin the air late at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then no one will wake up in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We can kill an entire city overnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it Operation: Poison Smog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And on that day, Shocker\Nwill conquer the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:07:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we test the death smog\Non one of the prisoners, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker does not look kindly on failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dokudalian, realize that death awaits\Nyou if your operation does not succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis! Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The plant is gone, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Big Sis!\N- Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe to run out into the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's got you all worked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think something bad\Nhappened to my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaves from my plant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a man's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my sister who went missing,\Nbut my plant went missing, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Its leaves looked like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord5\c&H96AAC7&\3c&H3D5044&}Jonan University Biochemistry Laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This leaf contains a tremendous\Namount of animal proteins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's less like a plant and more\Nlike a carnivorous beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are carnivorous\Nplants out there, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not very many. That's the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's toxic on top of that...\Nit's a dangerous plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So the man wearing this clothing\Nmight have been eaten by this plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?\NThat flower ate a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The florist is across that street.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:09:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait here. Go buy\Nyourselves some flowers, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll probably slip up\Nand give away the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll stand out less than you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, take Akko home\Nand hurry back, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like some flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri! I bet that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just how the little\Ngirl described it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You want that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear ladies of the\NTachibana Racing Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come right to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dine on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Koike said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:13:03.13,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari and Yuri are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"Store for rent"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they kidnapping\Nthose young women for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you go any faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one succumbed to the poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispose of her at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the way in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. They're making poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be Akko's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get going, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari! Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to feed\Nthem to Dokudalian?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a few brain cells\Nin your head, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:17:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt he's been captured, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been in there a long time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Think we should bust in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give him a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tobei. Mr. Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Those aren't our names.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato and the girls\Nare waiting for you in a certain location.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they came in disguise, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be more fun\Nto go along with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We can die after we see the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How very brave of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, show them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice work, Pops! Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:22:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All happiness to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.55,0:23:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Write to me a lot, okay, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.89,0:23:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Her husband's a lucky man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.81,0:23:31.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider defeated\Nthe man-eating flower monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.83,0:23:33.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and foiled her poison smog plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:37.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But what terrible thing\Nwould Shocker try next?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:40.71,Cont,,400,0,250,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)\fs70}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:43.02,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,476.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:45.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the steel monster Armadillong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:49.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The destructive steel beast's\Nplan to conquer Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:52.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,involves blowing up gasholders.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.98,0:23:55.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato and his\Nallies must put a stop to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:23:56.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:24:01.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Steel Monster Armadillong"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.14,0:24:01.10,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,210.389)}Steel Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.14,0:24:01.10,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs185\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,680.389)}Armadillong
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:10.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:13.55,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.55,0:24:15.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:18.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:20.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.93,0:24:22.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:24.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:26.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:28.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.49,0:24:34.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:37.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:41.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.83,0:24:45.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Man-Eating Flower,\NDokudalian."